      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I need help writing an email to a customer. They ordered a really expensive espresso machine (the Breville Barista Pro) but it's been two weeks late because of a glitch in our warehouse shipping system. They're pretty annoyed. Can you draft a professional apology that explains there was a logistics error and offers them a 15% discount on their next order to make up for it?",
