      "content": "Subject: Sincere Apologies for the Delay in Your Breville Barista Pro Order\n\nDear Valued Customer,\n\nI hope this message finds you well. I am writing to extend our sincerest apologies for the delay in the delivery of your Breville Barista Pro espresso machine. We understand how important this purchase is to you, and we deeply regret any inconvenience this delay may have caused.\n\nIt appears that a glitch in our warehouse shipping system has caused an unexpected delay in fulfilling your order. We are currently working diligently to resolve this issue and ensure that it doesn't happen again in the future. As a token of our appreciation for your patience and understanding, we would like to offer you a 15% discount on your next order with us.\n\nWe truly value your business and are committed to providing you with the best possible service. Thank you for your continued support, and we look forward to serving you again soon.\n\nWarm regards,\n\n[Your Name]\n[Your Position]\n[Your Contact Information]",
