      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start, but it feels a little bit like a generic template. Could you make it sound a bit more personal and \"human\"? Like, maybe instead of just saying \"a glitch in the system,\" you could describe the chaos of a warehouse error or how frustrating it is when things just go wrong behind the scenes without being too unprofessional?",
      "source": "evaluator"
